data.description: Brick End Unit Townhome! Must See! Featuring Hardwood Flooring, NEW Stainless Steel Appliances, NEW Water Heater & NEW HVAC.  Freshly Painted and Move In Ready.  Main Level with Large Living Room, Large Kitchen with NEW Stainless Steel Appliances and Breakfast Nook.  Slider leads to Privacy Fenced rear yard & Brick Patio.  Large Primary Bedroom with it's own Private Bathroom.  2 additional Bedrooms.  Fully Finished Basement with a Half Bathroom is perfect for Family Room / Game Room / Home Theater or Gym and large Utility Room with Storage.  2 Designated Parking Spaces. Within Walking Distance to Elementary School.  An abundance of Community Amenities - 2 Amazing Community Centers, 2 Fitness Centers, 4 Community Pools, 4 Tennis Coutts, Basketball, Tennis & Volley Ball Courts, Tot Lots throughout Community and a Baseball / Activities Field.  This Townhome is conveniently located near Major Highways, Close Proximity to Shopping Centers, Restaurants, and Fort Meade. The Marc Train located in Odenton is a 3 minute drive for easy access to Washington DC.  15 minutes to BWI.  Baltimore an easy 25 Minutes! Explore our State Capital, Annapolis with 20 minutes! This Location is the Best of Central Maryland!
